<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1946-10-15T17:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1946-07-28T18:00:00-05:00" n="180" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d180">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">C.P.(Gen)Doc.1.J.3.</note>
                        <head><hi rend="smallcaps">Article 16</hi></head>
                        <dateline>
                            <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-outside-research" calendar="gregorian" notAfter="1946-10-15T23:59:59+01:00" notBefore="1946-07-29T00:00:00+01:00">undated</date>
                        </dateline>
                        <p>Add after sub-paragraph 3 of paragraph 6 of Article 16 a new subparagraph
                                3(<hi rend="italic">a</hi>) reading as follows: <quote rend="blockquote">
                                <p>“<hi rend="italic">The legal rights and interest of the Greek
                                        Orthodox establishments</hi> (<hi rend="italic">communities,
                                        endowments or churches</hi>) <hi rend="italic">in Trieste
                                        shall be protected according to the provisions of Article 68
                                        of the present Treaty concerning similar establishments in
                                        Italy</hi>”.</p>
                            </quote></p>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>